{"tid":2125018,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國國防大臣華禮仕︰將重新審視外交、安全及國防政策　應對中俄威脅","createTime":"2020-07-26T01:26:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T01:52:53.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"099c7be3c49cd11bf2b96c7ba7521e28ec9fee70","tid":2125018,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T01:26:51.000Z","msg":"華禮仕在《星期日電訊報》表示，俄羅斯在原本屬於和平領域的太空，試驗具有武器特性的衛星，而中國亦正發展具攻擊性的太空武器，威脅國家安全，兩國的行為令英國要重新審視國家安全法律。<br />\n<br />\n另外，英國《星期日郵報》引述唐寧街消息人士報道，因應來自俄羅斯和中國的威脅，首相約翰遜計劃大幅修改《反叛國法》，包括修訂跟踪外國特工的間諜法和重寫《官方機密法》，以配合數碼時代，報道表示，今次是自叛國法律在1695年以來的最大修改。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539910-20200726.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539910-20200726.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLlCKRJWvDXkpEFRbHtszOvM%3D&h=6a4d7c0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539910-20200726.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fff46fa9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539910-20200726.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"ca6ac972e313bd23477850c1bdaf91184a121010","tid":2125018,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T01:28:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f382bdb8a8763ce890552269b9cc7c0c4717e4e","tid":2125018,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T01:29:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acec29abdf1d7095c6030a843ca69d4686861841","tid":2125018,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T01:29:24.000Z","msg":"169